name: Enter Data and Click on Submit for Out of Duty tab

testSteps.description: 1: Enter Data and Click on Submit for Out of Duty tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, tab=Out Duty/Tour, fromDate=29/09/2022, toDate=29/09/2022, outOfDutyType=Out Duty (Client Visit), enterReason=client visit, contactNumber=8888888888})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When User clicks on "Out Duty/Tour" Tab
Then Select "29/09/2022" From date and "29/09/2022" till Leave dates for Out Duty Tour
And Select "Out Duty (Client Visit)" from Type dropdown
Then Enter "8888888888" in "outing Contact Number" textbox
Then Enter "client visit" in "outing Reason" text box
Then Click on Submit button for Out of Duty Tab
And Verify Leave is submitted and "Out Duty/Tour request has been applied successfully." appears

userStory.narrative: This tests are for Apply module of MIS Beta
